other_tests.findings: There are bibasilar atelectasis, unchanged mild pneumobilia, unchanged linear hypodensity in the inferior right lobe of the liver, mild prominence of the pancreatic duct (up to 3.5 mm), peripancreatic fat stranding, and small amount of fluid in the left greater than right paracolic gutters.
Mildly coarsened hepatic echotexture, trace ascites, patent vasculature, no biliary dilatation, unchanged cystic lesion in the porta hepatis.
